*Hteo sam da se družim sa njim.(I wanted to hang out with him.)

*On je *hteo da odgovori na pitanje.(He wanted to answer the question.)

*Ona je *htela da se izvini.(She wanted to apologize.)

*Mi *hteli smo da idemo tamo.(We wanted to go there.)

*On je *htela da bude slobodan.(He wanted to be free.)

*Oni *hteshe da odu u šoping.(They wanted to go shopping.)